<section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-yellow-50 py-10">
  <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold pb-10 font-sans mx-5 text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
  <div class=" max-w-2xl mx-5 lg:mx-auto p-text pb-12">
    You might still have a few questions about pilot training at Sun City.  Discover answers to common inquiries about Sun City Aviation Academy's programs, facilities, and more. If you have any specific questions or need further information, please don't hesitate to reach out to us.
  </div>

  <div class="bg-white max-w-2xl mx-5 lg:mx-auto border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl mb-10">
		<ul class="shadow-box">					
		  <li class="relative border-b border-gray-200" x-data="{selected:null}">
			  <button type="button" class="w-full px-8 py-6 text-left" @click="selected !== 1 ? selected = 1 : selected = null">
				  <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
					  <span class="font-semibold text-lg">How long does it take to become a pilot?</span>
					  <span class="ico-plus"></span>
				  </div>
        </button>
			  <div class="relative overflow-hidden transition-all max-h-0 duration-700" style="" x-ref="container1" x-bind:style="selected == 1 ? 'max-height: ' + $refs.container1.scrollHeight + 'px' : ''">
				  <div class="p-6 p-text">
					  <p>This really depends on your availability, aptitude, and commitment. It can take anywhere from a few months to around a year.  If you train everyday, we've seen students get their private certiticate in one to two months.  If you're only able to dedicate a few days a week and train part time, expect to finish in 6 months to a year.  Training less often means that you will retain less information in the short term, but over time the training gets solidified.  Flight training is not a race and we need to make sure you are a safe and capable pilot.  Enjoy the journey and the only person you should be comparing yourself with is yourself.  A good pilot is always learning and training goes beyond and continues well after your private pilot certificate.</p>
				  </div>
			  </div>
		  </li>
		  <li class="relative border-b border-gray-200" x-data="{selected:null}">
			  <button type="button" class="w-full px-8 py-6 text-left" @click="selected !== 2 ? selected = 2 : selected = null">
				  <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
					  <span class="font-semibold text-lg">What are the eligibility requirements for becoming a pilot?</span>
					  <span class="ico-plus"></span>
				  </div>
				</button>
			  <div class="relative overflow-hidden transition-all max-h-0 duration-700" style="" x-ref="container2" x-bind:style="selected == 2 ? 'max-height: ' + $refs.container2.scrollHeight + 'px' : ''">
				  <div class="p-6 p-text">
					  <p>You can start training right away and there are no prerequisites to start.  However to solo and then go on to get your pilot certificate, you must meet the following prerequisites:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc ml-6">
              <li>be at least 17 years old</li>
              <li>be able to speak, read, and write English</li>
              <li>be able to obtain an FAA third class medical or higher</li>
            </ul>
				  </div>
			  </div>
		  </li>
      <li class="relative border-b border-gray-200" x-data="{selected:null}">
			  <button type="button" class="w-full px-8 py-6 text-left" @click="selected !== 3 ? selected = 3 : selected = null">
				  <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
					  <span class="font-semibold text-lg">How does one obtain a medical certificate?</span>
					  <span class="ico-plus"></span>
				  </div>
				</button>
			  <div class="relative overflow-hidden transition-all max-h-0 duration-700" style="" x-ref="container3" x-bind:style="selected == 3 ? 'max-height: ' + $refs.container3.scrollHeight + 'px' : ''">
				  <div class="p-6 p-text">
					  <p>One must register on <%= link_to "https://medxpress.faa.gov/medxpress/", "https://medxpress.faa.gov/medxpress/", target: "blank", class: "text-amber-500 hover:underline"%>  to fill out the application.  An instructor or staff member will make the medical appointment at one of the several local medical physicians we use.</p>
				  </div>
			  </div>
		  </li>
      <li class="relative border-b border-gray-200" x-data="{selected:null}">
			  <button type="button" class="w-full px-8 py-6 text-left" @click="selected !== 4 ? selected = 4 : selected = null">
				  <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
					  <span class="font-semibold text-lg">Do I need a college degree to be a pilot?</span>
					  <span class="ico-plus"></span>
				  </div>
				</button>
			  <div class="relative overflow-hidden transition-all max-h-0 duration-700" style="" x-ref="container4" x-bind:style="selected == 4 ? 'max-height: ' + $refs.container4.scrollHeight + 'px' : ''">
				  <div class="p-6 p-text">
					  <p>You do NOT need a college degree to become a pilot as most major airlines no longer require it. However, having a college degree can make you more competitive in the job market if you are looking to make a career out of aviation.</p>
				  </div>
			  </div>
		  </li>
      <li class="relative border-b border-gray-200" x-data="{selected:null}">
			  <button type="button" class="w-full px-8 py-6 text-left" @click="selected !== 4 ? selected = 4 : selected = null">
				  <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
					  <span class="font-semibold text-lg">What is a private pilot license?</span>
					  <span class="ico-plus"></span>
				  </div>
				</button>
			  <div class="relative overflow-hidden transition-all max-h-0 duration-700" style="" x-ref="container4" x-bind:style="selected == 4 ? 'max-height: ' + $refs.container4.scrollHeight + 'px' : ''">
				  <div class="p-6 p-text">
					  <p>A Private Pilot Certificate, also commonly known as a PPL (private pilot license), is one of the first certificates you obtain on your journey to becoming a licensed pilot. It allows you to be PIC (pilot in command) of an aircraft for personal and recreational purposes and also allows you to take passengers on board with you.  With a PPL, you cannot be compensated for flying as that would require a commercial certificate.</p>
				  </div>
			  </div>
		  </li>
      <li class="relative border-b border-gray-200" x-data="{selected:null}">
			  <button type="button" class="w-full px-8 py-6 text-left" @click="selected !== 4 ? selected = 4 : selected = null">
				  <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
					  <span class="font-semibold text-lg">Can I work for Sun City Aviation as a flight instructor after graduation?</span>
					  <span class="ico-plus"></span>
				  </div>
				</button>
			  <div class="relative overflow-hidden transition-all max-h-0 duration-700" style="" x-ref="container4" x-bind:style="selected == 4 ? 'max-height: ' + $refs.container4.scrollHeight + 'px' : ''">
				  <div class="p-6 p-text">
					  <p>Yes, after completing your Certified Flight Instructor Certificate you will be offered a guaranteed interview with our Chief Pilot. (All potential employees must be authorized to work in the United States).  Being a CFI is a great way to build flight time, while also providing a very valuable service of teaching others how to fly and bringing more people into aviation.</p>
				  </div>
			  </div>
		  </li>
      <li class="relative border-b border-gray-200" x-data="{selected:null}">
