				  <div class="p-6 p-text">
					  <p>No, all students should dress comfortably during their training sessions. We pride ourselves in being a relaxed family environment.  While wearing uniform and brandishing epaulets is not required at Sun City Aviation, if you feel that you can train better wearing uniform, you are free to do so.</p>
				  </div>
			  </div>
		  </li>
      <li class="relative border-b border-gray-200" x-data="{selected:null}">
			  <button type="button" class="w-full px-8 py-6 text-left" @click="selected !== 4 ? selected = 4 : selected = null">
				  <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
					  <span class="font-semibold text-lg">What will be the daily training schedule?</span>
